------------------------------------------Expression--------------------------------------------------
Mathematical + - / * %
String concatenation +
Logical && ||
Binary & | ^
Unary + - ! ~
Shift >> >>> <<
Comparison == > < >= <= (Note that < needs to be escaped as &lt;)
instanceof
Grouping ()
Literals - character, String, numeric, null
Cast
Method calls
Field access
Array access []
Ternary operator ?:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------